<section class="section readiness" id="readiness" data-reveal="section">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header" data-reveal>
      <p class="eyebrow">Production readiness</p>
      <h2>Operational guardrails that keep systems stable.</h2>
    </div>
      <div class="readiness-panel" data-reveal style="--delay: 80ms">
        <div>
          <p class="panel-label">Release readiness</p>
          <h3>We measure stability before every launch.</h3>
          <p class="section-body">
            Error budgets, performance baselines, and compliance checks are reviewed before release.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="panel-metrics">
          <div>
            <strong>98%</strong>
            <span>Builds pass gates</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>0.9s</strong>
            <span>P95 API latency</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <strong>7 days</strong>
            <span>Mean time to fix</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="readiness-charts" data-reveal style="--delay: 120ms">
        <div class="readiness-chart" data-chart="stability">
          <div class="chart-orbit" data-orbit="stability">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="chart-legend">
            <span>Release stability</span>
            <span class="chart-value" data-metric="stability">+22%</span>
          </div>
          <svg class="sparkline" viewBox="0 0 160 48" role="img" aria-label="Stability trend">
            <path
              data-sparkline
              d="M4 34 C 20 30, 38 26, 56 24 C 74 22, 92 16, 110 12 C 128 10, 146 12, 156 8"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="3"
              stroke-linecap="round"
            />
          </svg>
          <div class="chart-bars" data-bars aria-hidden="true">
            <span style="--bar: 0.3"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.42"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.56"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.64"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.7"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.78"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.86"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.9"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="chart-caption">Fewer failed releases with pre-flight gating.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="readiness-chart" data-chart="response">
          <div class="chart-orbit" data-orbit="response">
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
            <span></span>
          </div>
          <div class="chart-legend">
            <span>Incident response</span>
            <span class="chart-value" data-metric="response">-41%</span>
          </div>
          <svg class="sparkline" viewBox="0 0 160 48" role="img" aria-label="Response time trend">
            <path
              data-sparkline
              d="M4 12 C 22 16, 40 20, 58 24 C 76 28, 94 32, 112 36 C 130 38, 146 40, 156 42"
              fill="none"
              stroke="currentColor"
              stroke-width="3"
              stroke-linecap="round"
            />
          </svg>
          <div class="chart-bars" data-bars aria-hidden="true">
            <span style="--bar: 0.86"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.78"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.7"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.62"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.54"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.45"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.38"></span>
            <span style="--bar: 0.3"></span>
          </div>
          <p class="chart-caption">Faster response with clearer escalation playbooks.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    <div class="readiness-grid">
      <article class="card readiness-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 60ms">
        <h3>Observability &amp; SLOs</h3>
        <p>Metrics, tracing, and alerting aligned with clear performance targets.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card readiness-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 120ms">
        <h3>CI/CD guardrails</h3>
        <p>Secure pipelines with automated checks and deployment protection.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card readiness-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 180ms">
        <h3>Infrastructure as code</h3>
        <p>Repeatable environments, versioned changes, and predictable rollouts.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card readiness-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 240ms">
        <h3>Performance tuning</h3>
        <p>Load testing, bottleneck analysis, and optimizations for speed.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="card readiness-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 300ms">
        <h3>Documentation &amp; handoff</h3>
        <p>Clear system maps, runbooks, and onboarding that keep teams aligned.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
